<item>
            <title>[LU-11674] Lustre test framework is emitting invalid yaml</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11674</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The Lustre test framework is printing invalid yaml to the results.yml file. Autotest is setup to handle some of the bad YAML and will be improved to handle this situation better, however the Lustre test framework should sanitize the error strings it is printing. Attached is a sample of a recent results.yml file. See line 499&lt;/p&gt;</description>
